  /         item href="#" style=("text-align: left;")  Google +
  /     columns large="6" small="12" 
  /       h5 Contact Info:
  /       p Phone: 408-341-0600
  /       p
  /         | Email:
          a href="mailto:foundation@zurb.com"  foundation@zurb.com
